This paper discusses the privacy practices of websites, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cyber security (cs.CY). The analysis of the privacy practices involves data collection and tracking, which can also be related to social media (cs.SI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses security practices, which can be related to cryptography and security (cs.CC).
